%N A172078 a(n) = n*(16*n^2 + 3*n - 13)/6.
%C A172078 Generated by the formula n*(n+1)*(2*d*n-(2*d-3))/6 for d=8.
%C A172078 In fact, the sequence is related to A001107 by a(n) = n*A001107(n) - Sum_{k=0..n-1} A001107(k), and this is the case d=8 in the identity n*(n*(d*n-d+2)/2) - Sum_{k=0..n-1} k*(d*k-d+2)/2 = n*(n+1)*(2*d*n-2*d+3)/6. - _Bruno Berselli_, Dec 14 2010
